<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：网络延迟问题通常由DNS解析、路由跳变、TCP重传、带宽竞争或应用层超时配置不当引起，通过分层排查（物理层→网络层→传输层→应用层）可以快速定位根因。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="问题现象">问题现象</h2>
<p>线上服务出现间歇性超时：</p>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">Caused by: java.net.SocketTimeoutException: Read timed out
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    at java.net.SocketInputStream.socketRead0(Native Method)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">HTTP调用P99从50ms上升到800ms
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">部分请求正常，部分请求超时</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="影响范围">影响范围</h3>
<ul>
<li>服务间RPC调用超时率上升</li>
<li>用户体验下降，接口响应变慢</li>
<li>触发熔断，影响正常流量</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="排查过程">排查过程</h2>
<h3 id="第一步确认问题层级">第一步：确认问题层级</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">OSI分层排查：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">应用层（L7）→ HTTP/RPC超时配置是否合理？
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">传输层（L4）→ TCP连接是否正常？是否有重传？
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">网络层（L3）→ 路由是否跳变？是否有丢包？
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">链路层（L2）→ 网卡/交换机是否有错误？
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">物理层（L1）→ 带宽是否打满？光纤/网线是否正常？</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="第二步网络层排查命令">第二步：网络层排查命令</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-bash">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 1. 测试连通性和延迟</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">ping -c <span class="m">100</span> target-ip
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 关注：丢包率、延迟波动</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 2. 追踪路由路径</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">traceroute target-ip
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 关注：哪一跳延迟突增</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 3. 更详细的网络质量检测</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">mtr --report --report-cycles <span class="m">100</span> target-ip
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 关注：Loss%和Last列</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 4. TCP连接状态</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">ss -tan <span class="p">|</span> awk <span class="s1">&#39;{print $1}&#39;</span> <span class="p">|</span> sort <span class="p">|</span> uniq -c
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 关注：TIME_WAIT、CLOSE_WAIT数量</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="第三步传输层排查">第三步：传输层排查</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-bash">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 查看TCP重传率</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">cat /proc/net/snmp <span class="p">|</span> grep Tcp:
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># RetransSegs / OutSegs = 重传率，&gt;1%需关注</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 抓包分析（生产慎用）</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">tcpdump -i eth0 host target-ip -w capture.pcap
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># Wireshark分析：Filter tcp.analysis.retransmission</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 连接跟踪</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">conntrack -L <span class="p">|</span> grep target-ip <span class="p">|</span> wc -l
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 连接数是否超过阈值</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="第四步应用层排查">第四步：应用层排查</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 检查连接池配置</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">HikariConfig</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">config</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">HikariConfig</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">config</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">setConnectionTimeout</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">5000</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">   </span><span class="c1">// 获取连接等待时间</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">config</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">setMaxLifetime</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">1800000</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">      </span><span class="c1">// 连接最大生命周期</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">config</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">setMaximumPoolSize</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">50</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">       </span><span class="c1">// 最大连接数</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// HTTP客户端超时配置</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">RestTemplate</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">restTemplate</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">RestTemplate</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">SimpleClientHttpRequestFactory</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">factory</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">SimpleClientHttpRequestFactory</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">factory</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">setConnectTimeout</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">3000</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">     </span><span class="c1">// 建立连接超时</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">factory</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">setReadTimeout</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">5000</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">        </span><span class="c1">// 读取响应超时</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">restTemplate</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">setRequestFactory</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">factory</span><span class="p">);</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
